title: A State of Trance 400 - 59 of 72 hours including all club sets!
description:
This is 59 of the 72 hours of A State of Trance 400, broadcast live from April 16 - April 19, 2009.

Compiled from various sources including www.dirtyplanet.org and weloveatrance.com.
Files renamed and tagged by Eletriarnation, using mp3tag (www.mp3tag.com)
Tracklist thanks to the good people at forum.arminvanbuuren.com.

Missing:
Wuppertal/Birmingham Area 2 Live Shows (weren't broadcasted, I believe)
ASOT 004, Part 1 (my part 2 is an old recording, so that would be good too)
Robert Nickson's Guestmix (was it broadcasted? my tracklist says not)
Trance.Nu Feature
Randy Boyer's Guestmix
Genix's Guestmix
Stoneface and Terminal's Guestmix
Glenn Morisson's Guestmix
tyDi's Guestmix
Sophie Sugar's Guestmix
Leon Bolier's Guestmix
Martin Roth's Guestmix
Tenishia's Guestmix
ASOT 001, Part 1 (my part 2 is an old recording, so that would be good too)
Anything at the end, 20:00 on 04/19

Thanks everyone - enjoy, and my apologies for any mistakes or errors in this compilation!
If you know where I can get any of the sets that I am missing, PLEASE let me know in the comments for the torrent!

- Eletriarnation
